snippet.title: Aim Lab's NEW RANK SYSTEM!
snippet.description:
Aim Lab has a NEW Rank System and Profile tab! Learn about how your rank is calculated, and why we think the changes will help you improve even more.

Comment your rank below, and let us know your progress!

▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬

Become a better player & train your aim for free with Aim Lab on Steam
►  https://store.steampowered.com/app/714010/Aim_Lab
